      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HELLO ELSA (7) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in her quick 25.29 win at this track over 457m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Can measure up on top win three back. BURNSIDE BAMBI (3) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from seven starts. Placed last time (28.31) at Casino in a Grade 4/5, finishing second and beaten one length. Can hit the frame with the right run. MIGHTY SHAZAM (1) scored (25.61) last time out at this track in a Grade 5 and will break from box 1 for the first time. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Comes through a solid form race last start. Must be included in calculations. TRAVELLING DEAN (2) can sneak into the finish.",
